OL,3,CGovernment 'failed citizens' first
OL,4,Creport from Covid inquiry says
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Deputy Political
OL,7,FEditor Anushka Asthana and Health and
OL,8,FScience Produce Philip Sime
OL,10,FThe UK government and every devolved
OL,11,Fadministration ''failed their
OL,12,Fcitizens' by being ill-prepared for
OL,13,FCovid, resulting in more grief, untold
OL,14,Fmisery and economic turmoil than
OL,15,Fnecessary, according to the
OL,16,Fdevastating first conclusions of a
OL,17,Fmajor public inquiry into the pandemic.
