OL,3,CGovernment 'failed citizens' first
OL,4,Creport from Covid inquiry says
OL,6,FThe Chair, Baroness Hallett, made
OL,7,Fclear there was a failure of
OL,8,Fleadership across the board but named
OL,9,Ftwo former health secretaries, Matt
OL,10,FHancock and Jeremy Hunt.
OL,12,FLady Hallett has called on the Labour
OL,13,Fgovernment to implement urgent and
OL,14,F"fundamental reform," warning of
OL,15,Foverwhelming evidence that another
OL,16,Fpandemic, which could be even more
OL,17,Ftransmissible and lethal, is likely in
OL,18,Fthe near to medium future.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
