OL,3,CGovernment 'failed citizens' first
OL,4,Creport from Covid inquiry says
OL,6,F"It is not a question of 'if' another
OL,7,Fpandemic will strike but 'when'," she
OL,8,Fwarned, calling on the government to
OL,9,Fplace preparations for another health
OL,10,Fcrisis on a par with defence planning
OL,11,Ffor potential war.
OL,13,F"The primary duty of the state is to
OL,14,Fprotect its citizens from harm. It is,
OL,15,Ftherefore, the state's duty to ensure
OL,16,Fthat the UK is as properly prepared to
OL,17,Fmeet threats from a lethal disease as
OL,18,Fit is from a hostile force. Both are
OL,19,Fthreats to national security," she
OL,20,Fsaid.
