OL,3,CGovernment 'failed citizens' first
OL,4,Creport from Covid inquiry says
OL,6,FAnd yet the UK was "ill prepared" and
OL,7,F"lacked resilience," according to Lady
OL,8,FHallett's report, that claims public
OL,9,Fservices including health and social
OL,10,Fcare were running close to, if not
OL,11,Fbeyond, capacity with a slowdown in
OL,12,Fhealth improvement and widening health
OL,13,Finequalities.
OL,15,F"The Inquiry has no hesitation in
OL,16,Fconcluding that the processes,
OL,17,Fplanning and policy of the civil
OL,18,Fcontingency structures within the UK
OL,19,Fgovernment and devolved
OL,20,Fadministrations and civil services
OL,21,Ffailed their citizens."
