OL,3,CGovernment 'failed citizens' first
OL,4,Creport from Covid inquiry says
OL,6,FThe first 83,000 word report from the
OL,7,FCovid Inquiry also concluded that if
OL,8,Fthe country had been better prepared
OL,9,F"some of the financial and human cost
OL,10,Fmay have been avoided".
OL,12,FAmong ten recommendations is a call
OL,13,Ffor a UK-wide pandemic response
OL,14,Fexercise at least every three years
OL,15,Ffollowed by a report, a Cabinet level
OL,16,Fcommittee led by the prime minister or
OL,17,Fhis deputy, and implement a whole-
OL,18,Fsystem civil emergency strategy.
