OL,4,Creport from Covid inquiry says
OL,6,FShe also said the government should
OL,7,Fmove away from "reasonable worst case
OL,8,Fscenarios" and instead assess a wide
OL,9,Frange of scenarios.
OL,11,FAdditional recommendations include the
OL,12,Fuse of external "red-teams" who could
OL,13,Fscrutinise and challenge evidence and
OL,14,Fpolicies, and the formation of an
OL,15,Findependent statutory body for whole-
OL,16,Fsystem civil emergency preparedness,
OL,17,Fresilience and response.
