OL,4,Creport from Covid inquiry says
OL,6,FLady Hallett admitted that preparing
OL,7,Ffor a pandemic involves spending money
OL,8,Fon an event that "may never happen"
OL,9,Fbut said that must be carried out.
OL,10,F"The Covid-19 pandemic caused grief,
OL,11,Funtold misery and economic turmoil.
OL,12,FIts impact will be felt for decades to
OL,13,Fcome," she finds.
OL,15,F"There must be radical reform. Never
OL,16,Fagain can a disease be allowed to lead
OL,17,Fto so many deaths and so much
OL,18,Fsuffering."
