OL,3,CGovernment 'failed citizens' first
OL,4,Creport from Covid inquiry says
OL,6,FOutlining the cost of Covid, the
OL,7,Freport does not just highlight the
OL,8,F225,000 deaths in the UK, but also the
OL,9,Fmental illness, loneliness,
OL,10,Fdeprivation resulting from the
OL,11,Flockdown, as well as the impact on
OL,12,Fchildren's academic learning and
OL,13,Fsocial development.
OL,15,FLady Hallett, who has listened to more
OL,16,Fthan 100 hours of evidence, travelled
OL,17,Fthe country, received 20,000 responses
OL,18,Fto a consultation, and whose team has
OL,19,Fscoured 103,000 documents, said the UK
OL,20,Fbelieved it was one of the best
OL,21,Fprepared countries in 2019.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
