OL,3,CGovernment 'failed citizens' first
OL,4,Creport from Covid inquiry says
OL,6,F"In reality, the UK was ill-prepared
OL,7,Ffor dealing with a catastrophic
OL,8,Femergency, let alone the coronavirus
OL,9,F(Covid-19) pandemic that actually
OL,10,Fstruck."
OL,12,FAmong her criticisms were:
OL,14,FHallet said there had been a failure
OL,15,Fwithin the planning to account for pre-
OL,16,Fexisting inequalities and deprivation,
OL,17,Fand to appreciate the impact of such a
OL,18,Fcrisis on ethnic minority communities
OL,19,Fand others with poor health or
OL,20,Fvulnerabilities.
