OL,4,Creport from Covid inquiry says
OL,6,FLady Hallett adds: "The Secretaries of
OL,7,FState for Health and for Health and
OL,8,FSocial Care who adhered to the
OL,9,Fstrategy, the experts and officials
OL,10,Fwho advised them to do so, and the
OL,11,Fgovernments of the devolved nations
OL,12,Fthat adopted it, all bear
OL,13,Fresponsibility for failing to have
OL,14,Fthese flaws examined and rectified.
OL,16,F"This includes Mr Hancock, who
OL,17,Fabandoned the strategy when the
OL,18,Fpandemic struck, by which time it was
OL,19,Ftoo late to have any effect on
OL,20,Fpreparedness and resilience."
