OL,4,Creport from Covid inquiry says
OL,6,FLady Hallett's report includes
OL,7,Ftestimonies from victims, including
OL,8,Fthose who lost loved ones. Matt
OL,9,FFowler, co-founder of the Covid-19
OL,10,FBereaved Families for Justice, says
OL,11,Fthat only 10 people were able to
OL,12,Fattend his father's funeral and all
OL,13,Fwere socially distanced. But 300 lined
OL,14,Fthe streets for his procession.
OL,16,FJane Morrison from Scottish Covid
OL,17,FBereaved spoke of having to make the
OL,18,Fterrible decision of being with a
OL,19,Floved one in their final days and then
OL,20,Fisolating or attending a funeral.
